        "message": "=<p>Hi {{ $json.first_name }},</p><p>The average therapy practice with 20+ weekly sessions loses $400\u2013700/month to cancellations that never get backfilled. Not because there's no one to fill them \u2014 the waitlist exists. The backfill process is just slow and manual.</p><p>I help practices automate the waitlist-to-booking loop. When a slot opens, the next patient gets a text with a one-tap booking link. Most slots fill the same day.</p><p>One practice went from a 38% rebooking rate to 85% in 30 days. Nothing changed except the system.</p><p>Worth 20 minutes to see if the numbers make sense for {{ $json.practice_name }}?</p><p>Reggie Johnson<br>MAXXAM AI | reggie@maxxam.ai<br>Free diagnostic: <a href='https://tinyurl.com/maxxam-call'>https://tinyurl.com/maxxam-call</a></p><p>P.S. Curious how your practice scores on automation readiness? \u2192 <a href='https://maxxam.ai/quiz.html'>https://maxxam.ai/quiz.html</a></p>",
        "options": {
